the barren first wife who forgot to leave.

20:33.273 --> 20:35.984
No, you do not get to be
the wounded one.

20:36.068 --> 20:37.444
You fucking imposter.

20:37.527 --> 20:40.113
Imposter? Imposter -
this from the guy

20:40.197 --> 20:42.491
who hands out mixes of songs
he's never heard of.

20:42.574 --> 20:44.785
You hired an escort
to get your groove back,

20:44.868 --> 20:46.662
and then you got down
on your fucking knees

20:46.745 --> 20:48.038
